headline: BlackRock (NYSE:BLK) Declares Quarterly Dividend of US$5.21 Per Share
summary: BlackRock (NYSE:BLK) announced a quarterly cash dividend of $5.21 per share on May 15, 2025. During the past month, the company's share price rose 11%. The confirmation of the dividend could have bolstered investor confidence, reinforcing the stock's upward momentum alongside the broader market gains. Additionally, BlackRock's executive reshuffling and the launch of the iShares S&P 500 3% Capped ETF reflect strategic adaptations amid changing market dynamics. The positive market sentiment...
